4c62c85cb6e35d6b227a2e5db77","tid":737217,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34d280e75d9656a724f684d1690f79df8098296","tid":737217,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"條問題好清楚,亦都好基本,新手程度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"個test係重覆左好多次 <br />\n好多上完邏輯堂嘅學生 都答唔中佢嘅答案 <br />\n包括專研邏輯嘅研究生 一樣答錯  絕對唔係咩新手程度咁簡單 <br />\n（當然 material conditional 係好入門嘅野，<br />\n但個 test 有唔多地方引導人 唔會理解條件句做 material conditional) <br />\n<br />\n但個 test 係有問題 <br />\n近年已經有邏輯學家指出  個 test 冇明確表示佢背後嘅假設 <br />\n有本書叫 Human Reasoning and Cognitive Science<br />\n係由心理學家 Keith Stenning 同邏輯學家合寫 Michiel van Lambalgen<br />\n入面就詳盡分析 呢個 test 有乜問題"},{"pid":"9a840a28f3d62e2b5dec9535bd89a1042611e9e7","tid":737217,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"Wiki 亦有記載另一個邏輯學家 Johan van Benthem對呢個 test嘅批評：<br />\n<br />\nIn Wason's study, not even 10% of subjects found the correct solution. This result was replicated in 1993.<br />\n<br />\nSome authors have argued that participants do not read &quot;if... then...&quot; as the material conditional, since the natural language conditional is not the material conditional. (See also the paradoxes of the material conditional for more information.) However one interesting feature of the task is how participants react when the classical logic solution is explained:<br />\n<br />\nA psychologist, not very well disposed toward logic, once confessed to me that despite all problems in short-term inferences like the Wason Card Task, there was also the undeniable fact that he had never met an experimental subject who did not understand the logical solution when it was explained to him, and then agreed that it was correct."},{"pid":"cc00512bb1d79d9feb5c3d90e958f453faa2ee54","tid":737217,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"Vowel一定要雙數<br />\nConsonant 可以雙/單<br />\n<br />\nLoad到呢個concept就得，我估啲人未load到看衝動答左A2"},{"pid":"141590b57f6b41acaf82ec12f8c7a85715e292b9","tid":737217,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Vowel一定要雙數<br />\nConsonant 可以雙/單<br />\n<br />\nLoad到呢個concept就得，我估啲人未load到就*衝動答左A2</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8b21725897c2cb12a63f248de4856c043962b2af","tid":737217,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34d280e75d9656a724f684d1690f79df8098296","tid":737217,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"條問題好清楚,亦都好基本,新手程度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"我認同係新手程度，但都係易令人誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de116666ac55be0ff7664650615c10c5aafc1ee","tid":737217,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b21725897c2cb12a63f248de4856c043962b2af","tid":737217,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34d280e75d9656a724f684d1690f79df8098296","tid":737217,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"條問題好清楚,亦都好基本,新手程度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"我認同係新手程度，但都係易令人誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"解釋一下,我唔明點解會令人誤會"},{"pid":"22fe0dc0bc1757a093550b79091a63a2fd9f3642","tid":737217,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1de116666ac55be0ff7664650615c10c5aafc1ee","tid":737217,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b21725897c2cb12a63f248de4856c043962b2af","tid":737217,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34d280e75d9656a724f684d1690f79df8098296","tid":737217,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"條問題好清楚,亦都好基本,新手程度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"我認同係新手程度，但都係易